name: Fake Whac-a-Mole, come back Pikachu
description:
This is my first Html knock off indie game, created during late November 2021.

A lot of things don’t work, the screen is too long, points added only by clicking Pikachu, there are no negative points by clicking others, there is no stop button, the music and start button don’t sync well which you will have to click the music first then the start button … 😔 The game will end when the music end. 

I won’t fix it just to give it a nostalgic touch, but I may create a unity version of it soon.🙂 Enjoy 😊
